headline: CrowdStrike Holdings (NasdaqGS:CRWD) Expands AI Security with New NVIDIA Integration
summary: CrowdStrike Holdings (NasdaqGS:CRWD) recently announced a strategic integration of its Falcon Cloud Security platform with NVIDIA's LLM microservices, aiming to enhance AI application security. This collaboration might align with the company's share price increase of 35% over the last quarter, coinciding with positive market trends and a series of partnerships, including those with Microsoft and Portnox. headline: CrowdStrike Delivers Full Lifecycle Protection for LLMs to Enterprise AI Factories with NVIDIA
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, June 11, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced the integration of Falcon® Cloud Security with NVIDIA universal LLM NIM microservices and NeMo Safety, delivering full lifecycle protection for AI and over 100,000 large language models (LLMs) in collaboration with NVIDIA.
